ffuse X-ray spectrum. These results indicate that this AGN superwind is\ndriven by radiation pressure or was driven by a hot wind that has since\ndissipated despite on-going AGN activity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Feb 2020 19:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-04"}
