ificantly affect the electromagnetic signal from accreting neutron stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Feb 2020 23:32:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Aug 2020 14:25:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-02"}
