 CDW order is weak, there exist\nsignificant dynamic charge correlations in the optic phonon range at low\ndoping, near the edge of the superconducting dome.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Feb 2020 02:39:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 24 May 2020 03:10:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-26"}
