ults, we demonstrate the substantial gains of the\nproposed model-driven approach over GROUP LASSO and AMP when the number of\njointly sparse signals is not very large.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Feb 2020 05:25:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-10"}
