fy opportunities to apply this model to other\nstages of a browser's architecture as well as other performance- and\nenergy-critical devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Feb 2020 20:16:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-11"}
